es around the nature and quality of all in loco parentis relationships"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 41 0aCoach-athlete relationshipsxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aTouchxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aChild sexual abusexPrevention.1 aPiper, Heather,eeditor. 0aRoutledge research in sport, culture and society ;v35.  aGV 711 T68 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035237211  aGV 711 T68 2015wLCc1i0162035237211lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/11/2015  aGV 711 T68 2015wLCc1i0162035257938d9/28/2015e9/18/2015lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu3/19/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2003120304bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/68313236